---
---

<section class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-12">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">Key Features</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
        Built for teams that manage AI agents at scale.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 space-y-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-brand-600/50 transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Deterministic Output</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Same source always produces identical Markdown. No randomness. Hashes enable diffs that mean something.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 space-y-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-brand-600/50 transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Platform-Agnostic</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          One source, many targets. Compile fragments to Claude, Cursor, GitHub Copilot, internal docs, and more.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 space-y-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-brand-600/50 transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">CI Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          <code class="bg-gray-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-brand-400 text-sm">agentquilt check</code> fails the build on drift. Prevent stale agent files from slipping through.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 space-y-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-brand-600/50 transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Git-Native</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Fragments are files. Diffs are readable. No merge conflict hell. No manual conflict resolution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 space-y-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-brand-600/50 transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Validation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Schema-driven validation for agent metadata. Catch errors before compilation, not in production.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 space-y-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-brand-600/50 transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Evals & Testing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Built-in eval framework for regression testing. Ensure agent behavior changes are intentional.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
